'''John Aguiar''' ek Konknni kovi, borovpi, prosar madheomachi veokti ani kantaram rochpi zavn asa
zachim kantaram [[Akaxvanni]]<nowiki/>cher vitrailaeant chodd korun [[Goeant]] ani CD-ncher aikupak melltta.

== Songit ==
Tachem'' Viva'' ''Carnival'' kantar, songit bosovn rochlolem jem [[Mukesh Ghatwal]] hannem gailolem taka
Goenchea Karnaval vixoi kantar koxem 2012 vorsa vinchun kaddlolem, tannem 'Swatantra Goa', ek
desbhokti album-achem iogdan kelam zantunt panch Konknni ani tin Moratthi kantarancho aspav
asa jim [[Buyao Theatres]] Goem hannim prostut keleant.<ref>{{Cite web}}</ref>

Aguiar hannem ek  bhokti git  Somi Gonexa <ref>{{Cite web}}</ref>  voir toiar kelam zachem songitachem rochop ani gavop Mukesh Ghatwal hannem kelam, jem  Konknni  bhaxent poilem zavn asa.<ref>{{Cite web}}</ref>

[[Akaxvanni]] soddun tanchim kantaram CD-ncher loukik zaleat zoxe porim ''Valley of Colorz'', E''k
Natem, Buyao Rocks'' tech porim bhokti gitancheo CD zoxe porim Grateful to Jesus<ref>{{Cite news}}</ref>  ani ''Hey, Damodara''  hea famad songit rochpi Siddhnath Buyao hannem toiar kelam. Tachem ek kantar Somi Damodar,<ref>{{Cite web}}</ref> hacher asa zo Dokxinn Goenchea Moddganvchi ek bhokt zavn asa, ek ekoddem kantar jem Dilip Vaze hannem rochun tem Samiksha Bhobe hannim gailam..

''Planning Devachem''<ref>{{Cite news}}</ref>, hea Konknni filmant tacho koalkar koso aspav zala zachi poili dakhovn Janer
2018 Moddganv, Goem hanga zali..

== Kovita ==
Tannem Konknni kovitechim char pustokam ani ek Inglixint nobondanchem pustok boroileant.
Sodheak, to anik ek pustokacher vavurta jem Konknnchea Romi lipient astolem. Tannem sabar lekh
thollavea potram khatir somajik vixoiancher lekh boroileat. Mungllurchea Kolangonna, khatir taka
boreantlim borim kantaram ghoddpa khatir tachi nemnnuk zaloli Jagotik Songit Tosripam 2010 vorsa
ani taka [[Konknni Bhaxa Monddol |Konknni Bhaxa Monddol]] hachem Rock Barreto Sahitik Tosrip favo 2017 vorsa tachea  ''Olyo
Yadi'' khatir favo zalam.

== Tosripam ==
2011 vorsa taka  ''Gulab-''Vorsantlo Borovpi tosrip favo zalam, ani  ''The Navhind Times'' hannim taka
Ex-NCC Achiever Award for Literature 2012 vorsa bhettoilam.ani to Bhovmanacho Komponi Home
Guards sonsthecho zavn asa. Taka  Goenchea  Mukhel Montreachem Bhangra Podok Home
Guards hachea Tokhnnaieche Seve khatir Dezembr 2007 vorsa dilam.

Vevsaient, to ek Goem Rajeachea Mhaiti ani Porgottnni vibhagacho odhikari asa.. Aguiar ek potrkar
tachea kolejichea disam pasun asa, ani tacho sombond zoxe porim ''Herald'', ''West Coast Times'', ani
heram kodde zala.

